data.description: Welcome to this beautiful home that seamlessly combines comfort, elegance, and contemporary living.  This meticulously maintained 5-bedroom, 4.5-bath residence, only a few years old, boasts the allure of new construction and includes a rare 3-car garage.  Nestled in the sought-after Greer area, this home offers over 4000 sqft of living space.  Upon entering, you'll be greeted by the open and spacious layout, accentuated by high ceilings and an abundance of natural light, creating an inviting atmosphere.  The heart of the home, the gourmet kitchen, is a culinary masterpiece featuring stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, a subway tile backsplash, and stunning grey cabinetry.  There is also a butler's pantry leading into a formal dining room with a gorgeous coffered ceiling.  The expansive living room, complemented by a cozy fireplace, is perfect for both festive gatherings and intimate winter nights.  The main level graciously hosts a spacious primary suite, seamlessly connected to the living room and kitchen.  The primary suite offers a tranquil retreat with a generously sized bedroom, walk-in closet, and an en-suite bathroom complete with a soaking tub, separate shower, and his/her vanities.  Upstairs, discover four additional bedrooms, two of which share a Jack and Jill bathroom, while a third enjoys its own private bathroom.  An another plus is the large upstairs bonus room, ideal for various uses such as a game room or home theater.  Other modern amenities include tankless water heater, remote controlled air conditioning, and a security system.  Step outside to the screened porch and patio in the backyard lined with Frazier firs for privacy, providing a serene place to relax.  Conveniently situated in the popular Eastside of Greenville within the Riverside School District and only a few minutes from charming downtown Greer, this home perfectly balances space and style.  Schedule your private tour today and unlock the boundless possibilities of making 212 Granito Drive your dream home!
